# eth_getUserOperationReceipt

request example

```json
{
  "jsonrpc": "2.0",
  "id": 0,
  "method": "eth_getUserOperationReceipt",
  "params": [
    "0x3356e0dc28511337610d66f2c9e957b9512f8e360447085586eaadece2bf2bdb"
  ]
}
```
